         <div type="translation">
            <p> For Apollinaris, freedwoman of Calvisius and Maia, [who] lived for 18 years;
               Publius Calvisius Hymen, freedman of Publius and a women, [and] Maia Auge, freedwoman
               of a woman, made [this] for himself/herself (resp.) and for their own.</p>
            <p>Aulus Popilius Chrestio, freedman of Aulus; Aulus Popilius Chresimus, freedman of
               Aulus; Popilia Lachesis, freedwoman of Aulus.</p>
         </div>
